{
  "texts": [
    "S and M indicate MCQs with one single correct answer and multiple correct answers, respectively.",
    "Full represents the overall accuracy of both types of MCQs.",
    "Bold numbers indicate that the performance improves against the corresponding pre-SFT model.",
    "Table 1, these findings underscore the effectiveness of enhancing the domain-specific capabilities of LLMs through SFT.",
    "Additionally, for the previously strongest subject, S2 (professional knowledge), LLMs maintained competitive performance, with an average accuracy of 50.1%, similar to the pre-SFT average accuracy of 50.2%."
  ]
